<dl id="n42024b"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n42" href="#n42024b">N42 (VI.B.31)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n42all.htm#n42024b"> 24(b)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> fallen from the / lips of Lamb</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">repeat into the ears of that redeemed sinner the sentence just fallen from the lips of the Lamb whose blood cleanses us from all our sins, say unto him, &ldquo;Thy sins are forgiven.&rdquo; <small> Chiniquy, <a name="CPWC" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#CPWC"><cite title="source">The Priest The Woman and The Confessional</cite></a> (n.d.) 115</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
